title: Syllabus mentioned in ERP
text: Estimation of amino acid, protein, total protein, phospho-protein, from different biological samples; electrophoresis; effect of pH temperature; substrate concentration; concentration of enzyme; Km; Vmax and Ki determination of half-life period of the enzyme and effect of protein denaturant.
